        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="C6wBBSbeSvJVTJ41NMnE-137" edge="1" parent="1" source="sozHreB-E5EmVtEhju2Q-28" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;exitX=0.75;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;strokeWidth=4;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" target="C6wBBSbeSvJVTJ41NMnE-138">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="1333" y="5192" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="C6wBBSbeSvJVTJ41NMnE-139" edge="1" parent="1" source="C6wBBSbeSvJVTJ41NMnE-138" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;strokeWidth=4;" target="C6wBBSbeSvJVTJ41NMnE-129">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="C6wBBSbeSvJVTJ41NMnE-138" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#D5E8D4;gradientColor=#b3b3b3;strokeColor=#666666;gradientDirection=east;" value="&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 50px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;SUBSCRIBER SRV&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="183" width="593" x="1977" y="4620" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="C6wBBSbeSvJVTJ41NMnE-141" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#0050ef;fontColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#001DBC;" value="&lt;p data-start=&quot;233&quot; data-end=&quot;307&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 30px;&quot;&gt;WE SEPARATE &lt;span data-start=&quot;245&quot; data-end=&quot;270&quot;&gt;LIKE COUNT MANAGEMENT&lt;/span&gt; FROM &lt;span data-start=&quot;276&quot; data-end=&quot;306&quot;&gt;USER-LIKE STATE MANAGEMENT&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 30px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;FOR EACH VIDEO, WE MAINTAIN A &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-start=&quot;339&quot; data-end=&quot;361&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;TOTAL LIKE COUNTER&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt; THAT IS USED ONLY TO DISPLAY THE NUMBER OF LIKES ON THE UI&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 30px;&quot;&gt;WHEN A USER CLICKS &lt;span data-start=&quot;443&quot; data-end=&quot;451&quot;&gt;LIKE&lt;/span&gt;, THE TOTAL LIKE COUNT IS INCREMENTED AND THE LIKE ICON IS SHOWN AS ACTIVE.WHEN THE USER CLICKS &lt;span data-start=&quot;550&quot; data-end=&quot;560&quot;&gt;UNLIKE&lt;/span&gt;, THE TOTAL LIKE COUNT IS DECREMENTED AND THE ICON IS RESET TO THE INACTIVE STATE.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 30px;&quot;&gt;TO SCALE FOR HIGH-TRAFFIC AND VIRAL VIDEOS, THE LIKE COUNTER IS &lt;span data-start=&quot;708&quot; data-end=&quot;743&quot;&gt;SHARDED USING A HASH OF USER_ID&lt;/span&gt;, SO THAT CONCURRENT LIKE REQUESTS ARE DISTRIBUTED ACROSS MULTIPLE SHARDS AND DO NOT CREATE A HOTSPOT ON A SINGLE COUNTER.AN AGGREGATED TOTAL COUNTER IS MAINTAINED SO THE UI CAN READ THE LIKE COUNT USING A SINGLE FAST LOOKUP.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 30px;&quot;&gt;TO DETERMINE WHETHER A USER HAS ALREADY LIKED A VIDEO, WE STORE THE &lt;span data-start=&quot;1041&quot; data-end=&quot;1071&quot;&gt;USER-LIKE STATE SEPARATELY&lt;/span&gt; FROM THE COUNTERS.THIS IS DONE BY STORING A &lt;span data-start=&quot;1119&quot; data-end=&quot;1157&quot;&gt;SINGLE KEY PER (USER_ID, VIDEO_ID)&lt;/span&gt; IN REDIS, WHICH INDICATES THAT THE USER HAS LIKED THE VIDEO.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 30px;&quot;&gt;TO CONTROL MEMORY USAGE AT SCALE, THIS USER-LIKE STATE IS STORED IN REDIS &lt;span data-start=&quot;1294&quot; data-end=&quot;1323&quot;&gt;WITH A TTL (TIME-TO-LIVE)&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br&gt;REDIS THEREFORE HOLDS ONLY &lt;span data-start=&quot;1354&quot; data-end=&quot;1392&quot;&gt;RECENT AND ACTIVE USER-LIKE STATES&lt;/span&gt;, WHILE OLDER OR INACTIVE LIKES AUTOMATICALLY EXPIRE AND ARE REMOVED FROM MEMORY.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 30px;&quot;&gt;THE &lt;span data-start=&quot;1479&quot; data-end=&quot;1519&quot;&gt;DATABASE REMAINS THE SOURCE OF TRUTH&lt;/span&gt; AND STORES ALL USER-LIKE RELATIONS PERMANENTLY.&lt;br data-start=&quot;1567&quot; data-end=&quot;1570&quot;&gt;WHEN A REDIS KEY EXPIRES OR IS MISSING, THE SYSTEM CAN FALL BACK TO THE DATABASE, REPOPULATE REDIS IF NEEDED, AND CONTINUE SERVING THE REQUEST WITHOUT AFFECTING THE USER EXPERIENCE.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 30px;&quot;&gt;WHEN A USER OPENS A VIDEO, THE SYSTEM FIRST CHECKS REDIS TO DETERMINE WHETHER THE USER HAS LIKED THE VIDEO.IF THE KEY EXISTS, THE LIKE ICON IS SHOWN AS ACTIVE.IF THE KEY DOES NOT EXIST FALLS BACK TO THE DATABASE FOR CONFIRMATION.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="985" width="1942" x="467" y="7354" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="C6wBBSbeSvJVTJ41NMnE-142" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 50px;&quot;&gt;HOW LIKE WORK&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="132" width="587" x="619" y="7359" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="C6wBBSbeSvJVTJ41NMnE-143" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=#001DBC;fillColor=#0050ef;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontColor=#ffffff;" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 30px;&quot;&gt;SUBSCRIBER ALSO WORK LIKE LIKE MODEL GIVEN IN END&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="185" width="347" x="2395" y="4833" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="C6wBBSbeSvJVTJ41NMnE-144" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=#001DBC;fillColor=#0050ef;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontColor=#ffffff;" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 30px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;HOW LIKE WORK GIVEN BELOW HOW IT HANDLE MULTIPLE LIKES&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="172" width="267" x="2913" y="3645" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
